[Student "S"]
{EAST has 13 points but she has to pass. 
She cannot Double without support for \Hs. 
She cannot bid 1NT without 2 more points. 
She cannot overcall 2\C with a terrible suit like that.

And WEST of course must also pass.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "2"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "E:975.AT5.AT94.JT9 KQJ842.Q2.Q87.83 A6.9843.632.K654 T3.KJ76.KJ5.AQ72"]
